ALIGN ON EQUALS

        h^2 + 49 \amp = 625 \amp\amp \blert{\text{Subtract 49 from both sides.}}
            h^2 \amp = 576 \amp\amp \blert{\text{Extract roots.}}
            h \amp = \pm \sqrt{576} \amp\amp \blert{\text{Simplify the radical.}} 
            h \amp = \pm 24 

